{"name":"Philip III","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Vanguards, Ft. Bill","alignment":"Lawful Neutral","hitDice":"20","armorName":"plate","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":8,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"150 (20d8 + 60)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"20","dexPoints":"12","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"8","wisPoints":"14","chaPoints":"20","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"7","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Action Surge","desc":"[MON] gains an extra action once per short rest."},{"name":"Combustion","desc":"If [MON] sets a creature on fire, they take [1d4] fire damage at the start of their turn for 3 turns. This can be put out with an action or healing"},{"name":"Great Weapon Master","desc":"[MON] can take -5 to his attack rolls to deal an extra +10 damage."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"[MON] makes two attacks with his empowered greatsword."},{"name":"Breaking Dawn","desc":"Phil swings his blazing greatsword. [STR ATK + 2] to hit, one target. _Hit:_ [STR 2D6] slashing damage. If the creature is burning, this attack automatically crits. Otherwise, this sets a creature on fire."},{"name":"Fireball","desc":"[MON] hurls a **DC [CHA SAVE]** Fireball. All creatures hit by the Fireball are set on fire."},{"name":"Blazing Spark","desc":"**[Recharge 5-6]** [MON] summons a pheonix that burns anything and everything within a 15 x 60 ft. line. All creatures hit are set on fire and take [8d6] fire damage (halved upon a successful **DC [CHA SAVE]** dex save)."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Smoldering Concord","desc":"[MON] rallies allies within a 10ft radius. Until the end of their next turn, their melee and ranged weapon attacks set the target creature on fire."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"con","order":2}],"skills":[{"name":"athletics","stat":"str"},{"name":"intimidation","stat":"cha"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"persuasion","stat":"cha"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Phil","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":3,"damage":[]}